{
  "stem": "717.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I didn't have a birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I think Regina did then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I didn't have any papers at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we registered to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the United States had a quota system.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were on the Polish quota.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Even though I ran away from Poland, I'll be originally born in Poland all of my life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I was on the Polish quota.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "At that time, it was very strictly observed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But finally, when-- I think I got some papers from Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I think I got my birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I had two witnesses from before the war, went to the-- to the police station, to the city hall, we had enough papers to have the legal marriage.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So in 1950, I think-- This date, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I think in June 1950 we had our legal papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We got the marriage certificate and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But something decided for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war in Korea broke out in 1950.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I figured out in my logic, well, at that time, distance still made a big difference.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I looked at a map, Australia was somewhere in the bottom, the other end of the world.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I figured that the United States is gonna be involved no matter how in that war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Australia might not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wanted to be as far away from Europe or anything that has anything to do with wars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Melbourne was the furthest point in Australia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, that movie from Nevil Shute about the last day of the world was filmed in Melbourne as it being the last city in the world.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Australia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All my friends went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Family, I didn't have anywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was with my friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in Australia 15 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
